mv - move or rename paths
Executable: /bin/mv.sh
Alias: mv

DESCRIPTION
  Moves or renames files and
  directories.

USAGE
  mv <source> <destination>
  mv <source> [source...]
     <directory>

NOTES
  Wildcards are expanded
  through fs.find().
  Moving multiple sources
  requires an existing
  destination directory.
  Drive roots and read-only
  sources are rejected.
